  <h1 class="first"><span class="t">T</span><small><span class="firstLine">he colophon is a brief description of the 'making of' a book.</span><span class="small"><sup id="fnref:1.1" class="footnote"><a href="/about#fn:1.1">[1]</a></sup> The making of <em>this</em> book has been far from brief; it involved not only the research and writing of the content, but also the design and development of this website.</span></small>
  </h1>
